#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Įvadas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&dolphin; is &kde;'s default file manager. It aims to improve usability "
#| "at the user interface level. &dolphin; focuses only on being a file "
#| "manager whereas &konqueror;, which was &kde;'s default file manager in "
#| "&kde; 3 and can still be used for file management, is a universal viewer "
#| "for many file types."
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is &plasma;'s default file manager. It aims to improve usability "
"at the user interface level. &dolphin; focuses only on being a file manager "
"whereas &konqueror;, which was &kde;'s default file manager in &kde; 3 and "
"can still be used for file management, is a universal viewer for many file "
"types."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; yra &kde; failų tvarkyklė, siekianti naudotojo sąsają padaryti "
"kiek galima patogesne naudojimui. &dolphin; kuriama tik tam, kad tvarkytų "
"failus, tuo tarpu kai &konqueror;, kuris buvo pagrindinė failų tvarkyklė "
"&kde; 3 laikais, leidžia ir tvarkyti failus, ir peržiūrėti įvairių tipų "
"failų turinį bei naršyti internete (jūs ir dabar galite naudoti &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This development approach allows for concentrating on optimizing the user "
#| "interface for the specific task of file management."
msgid ""
"This design approach allows the developers to concentrate on optimizing the "
"user interface for the specific task of file management."
msgstr ""
"Toks požiūris į programos kūrimą leidžia susikoncentruoti ties failų "
"tvarkymų ir būtent jį optimizuoti, neprarandant failų tvarkymo paprastumo "
"vardan kito funkcionalumo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Please report any problems or feature requests to the &dolphin; author "
#| "via the bug report dialog. This is accessible either from the "
#| "<guibutton>Configure and control &dolphin;</guibutton> button at the "
#| "right of the toolbar in the default mode without menu bar; or from "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu of the application, if the menubar is "
#| "shown."
msgid ""
"Please report any problems or feature requests to the &dolphin; author via "
"the bug report dialog. This is accessible either from the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right of the toolbar in the "
"default mode without menubar; or from <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu of the "
"application, if the menubar is shown."
msgstr ""
"Praneškite apie problemas ir pageidaujamą funkcionalumą &dolphin; autoriui "
"per klaidų registravimo dialogą. Jį galite pasiekti paspaudę dešinėje "
"įrenkinės pusėje pradiniame meniu neturinčiame variante esantį mygtuką "
"<guibutton>Konfigūruoti ir valdyti &dolphin;</guibutton> arba parinkę meniu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pagalba</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pranešti apie ydą...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

